text: Zell is a municipality in the district of Winterthur in the canton of Zurich in Switzerland. It is in the upper Töss Valley. ==Villages== Garten, Kollbrunn, Lettenberg, Rämismühle, Rikon, Schoren, Zell, Oberlangenhard and Unterlangenhard ==Gallery== File:Zell Dorfplatz 2.JPG|Zell File:Rikon IMG 2782.JPG|Rikon File:Zell ZH Kirche.JPG|Church of Zell ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website of Zell Category:Municipalities in Winterthur
